        "action": "Ban HGV overtaking on motorways to help improve safety and traffic flow",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "The Government should introduce a ban on heavy goods vehicles overtaking on motorways, with exceptions only for passing stationary or broken-down vehicles. This should be supported by clear signage, effective enforcement, penalties, and alignment with road safety practices in parts of Europe.",
